Program: Discovery
Title: World Oceans Day
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxf3
Last Broadcast Date: 04 June 1999
The programme celebrates World Oceans Day with a look at the life under the waves. A look at the diversity of small creatures that can only be seen with a microscope, creatures that live in extremely hot or cold parts of the world's oceans and how shellfish have been able to reproduce successfully for millions of years. Show less